data.description: Welcome to your new home, located in the amazing Town of Gilbert, This charming 4-bed 2-bath home offers a perfect blend of location, large, corner homesite, convenience to amenities & quiet living, The open-concept layout allows the great room to flow seamlessly into the exquisit kitchen which includes large Island, high-end appliances, upgraded cabinets, HUGE walk-in PANTRIES & granite countertops. The primary suite is a true retreat with a roomy walk-in closet & a large, open bath. all this with 3 additional spacious bedrooms, 3-car garage & oversized laundry room, Enjoy the outdoor oasis with oversized covered patio, & sparkling, fenced pool AND with-in walking distance to Gilbert schools, near to shopping, restaurants & in a great community, come take a look you won't be disappointed
